tweet: Update on the #TuckerFire in Modoc County: 14,217 acres have burned & the fire is 10% contained. Growth slowed yesterday, but increased winds today could lead to more erratic behavior. There are no evacuation orders in effect at this time.  https://www.google.com/amp/s/amp.sacbee.com/news/state/california/fires/article233333627.html …

Residents be advised: the #TuckerFire in Modoc County spread rapidly yesterday and is up to 11,000 acres. There are no evacuation orders in effect at this time, but stay tuned to the Modoc County Sheriff’s Department for updates as necessary. https://www.klamathfallsnews.org/news/tucker-fire-explodes-to-11000-acres …
